normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c8c4bdcc13150f30433dfba8ad17e0d63c3c8f","tid":283222,"uid":41769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲律賓出名燒雞<br />\n但係豬紅個汁好黑好酸<br />\n見到都想反胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw我最唔順係個種椰油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個喺尼泊爾菜"},{"pid":"927fa9704154f684497b574d15bf3307c6289efe","tid":283222,"uid":41769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T14:54:59.000Z","msg":"菲律賓菜幾好食<br />\n<br />\n炸豬手<br />\nsisig<br />\n芋頭葉<br />\ngarlic rice<br />\n椰奶魚<br />\nsinigang (酸酸地嘅湯)<br />\n<br />\n椰汁班蘭芭菲<br />\ncalamansi juice<br />\n<br />\n全部都幾好味"},{"pid":"e005ceca50737fc1fd1719aca8b51538e51a9a67","tid":283222,"uid":110699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T15:06:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菲律賓菜同英國菜一樣出名難食<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個國家都係美食沙漠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實講人定菜。。。。。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n兩個國家啲人都係廚神級<br />\n<br />\n所以英國人就惟有派兵殖民<br />\n而菲律賓人就掉晒啲女人出去學其他菜"},{"pid":"170b378f06526b5bc8b90dd2188f7dba3918b5ea","tid":283222,"uid":43141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T16:17:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲律賓菜幾好食<br />\n<br />\n炸豬手<br />\nsisig<br />\n芋頭葉<br />\ngarlic rice<br />\n椰奶魚<br />\nsinigang (酸酸地嘅湯)<br />\n<br />\n椰汁班蘭芭菲<br />\ncalamansi juice<br />\n<br />\n全部都幾好味</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22231518179522cf351d6787278cbced9b4b44fb","tid":283222,"uid":94182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T17:23:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blo